Key: Key this action is bound to
OverrrideState: EInputActionState::Enabled means that the state isn't overriden and the games dynamic control will work
HoldRollbackTime:
Time (in seconds) for hold progress to go from 1.0 (completed) to 0.0.
If the hold interaction was interrupted, then hold progress starts to roll back decreasing its value.
Set to 0.0 to disable the rollback functionality.
OverrideBrush: Override the brush specified by the Key Display Data
